{"id": 2278, "genre": 1001, "title": "相处初期，你会通过哪些细节判断对方是否有好感？", "description": "能不能跟一个人发展恋爱关系，这通常不需要明确表态就能看出来。（题图来自：iStock）", "record_count": 4721, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180412100835YIqN06OWZFcdf8kw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-12T03:06:48Z", "options": [{"id": 275456, "content": "单身的我，就是要点进来", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300175}, {"id": 277248, "content": "语言举止", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322752}, {"id": 275457, "content": "是否发自内心关心过对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286483}, {"id": 275458, "content": "指甲是否干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182174}, {"id": 275714, "content": "一个眼神和表情，足以", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794147}, {"id": 283906, "content": "看回复速度咯，还有能坚持陪你聊到几点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1003171}, {"id": 275459, "content": "小小的撒一下娇试试就知道了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 275460, "content": "即使冷场了，对方也会主动找话题。", "image": "img/option/option/20180412220937sPrMCv4JB9UAOxim.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894504}, {"id": 277508, "content": "抢着买单，我会说好吧既然你那么义不容辞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487377}, {"id": 275461, "content": "每次远远的看见就想跑过去打招呼?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312919}, {"id": 275462, "content": "单身又没人撩的我，为什么要点进来...", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312934}, {"id": 275463, "content": "不粘人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084711}, {"id": 276232, "content": "单身的我金凯悦转转", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318779}, {"id": 275465, "content": "张小小在看吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036197}, {"id": 276233, "content": "单身的我进来转转", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318779}, {"id": 275467, "content": "单身的我看得津津有味", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129559}, {"id": 275723, "content": "就算全中也不一定就会喜欢。更重要的是如何区分别人是否喜欢和我自作多情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314911}, {"id": 275468, "content": "谈恋爱不谈哲学，太幼稚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 34186}, {"id": 275469, "content": "主动找话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147893}, {"id": 275470, "content": "有兴趣、不敷衍\n最好还能兴趣相投", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312976}, {"id": 275726, "content": "过马路手下意识拉着我 过去以后马上松开", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314992}, {"id": 275471, "content": "是否主动约着下次见面，或者主动联系聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312977}, {"id": 275472, "content": "熊果果，我想不断的找话题，和你一直聊下去，聊到老。晚安！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037576}, {"id": 275474, "content": "是否愿意进行对等的交流而非单方面的好奇与关心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989435}, {"id": 275475, "content": "微表情吧，还有语气和待人接物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294982}, {"id": 275731, "content": "并没有在一起，不过他短信主动找我，说些你难受我也难受之类的话我就认为他对我有好感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315043}, {"id": 277011, "content": "哎我去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321951}, {"id": 288275, "content": "见过面后，会不会回去继续缠着你聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378608}, {"id": 275476, "content": "在没有语言交流的时候会不会偷偷端详你的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312945}, {"id": 275477, "content": "用心感受心与心的距离，感情就像齿轮，需要磨合，性格是有长有短。", "image": "img/option/option/201804122325235ELC1JHkv8qFK4Xz", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310582}, {"id": 275478, "content": "一看到你就扑腾扑腾跑过来，像是要跑进你心里???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1299471}, {"id": 275734, "content": "一见面就笑，字里行间全是你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315112}, {"id": 275479, "content": "相处时的感觉和对方看你的眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312963}, {"id": 275480, "content": "过马路的时候会不会帮我看着车，顺便有点肢体接触。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313001}, {"id": 276248, "content": "各种理由约下一次见面，聊天中幽默风趣，并分享着所有他觉得有意思的事情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318583}, {"id": 275481, "content": "送到小区，是不是一直看着你走进去直到看不见为止", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1232682}, {"id": 275738, "content": "困到眼睛睁不开还和他一直聊下去\n只要手机一震动马上就清醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315124}, {"id": 276506, "content": "不经意间的摸头?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315565}, {"id": 275483, "content": "通过眼神接触进行判断吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281880}, {"id": 275739, "content": "好吃的都给你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722823}, {"id": 275484, "content": "很简单，一见面会不由自主的傻笑~我是男生，以前会傻笑那个……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301948}, {"id": 275485, "content": "很认真的听你说话 并开导你", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1307230}, {"id": 276509, "content": "有好感怎么样，早安说了晚安到了，还是决绝的分手，头也不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54121}, {"id": 275486, "content": "和我说话时看我的眼神，以及一些肢体语言。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311974}, {"id": 278814, "content": "用各种理由增加和你互动的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575362}, {"id": 275487, "content": "在与她交谈或者在做某一事被她看的时候会感觉浑身不自在……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1313043}, {"id": 275488, "content": "会跟你分享生活点滴", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817736}, {"id": 275489, "content": "他（她）看你的眼神和是否及时回复你的消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287479}, {"id": 276001, "content": "带你上分", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166138}, {"id": 275490, "content": "看头发，计算微动作，拢头发就是最直接的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689835}]}